snippet.title: Best VGM 1878 - Digimon Story : Cyber Sleuth - Kuremi Detective Agency
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Vita / PS4
Digimon Story : Cyber Sleuth (2015)
Kuremi Detective Agency
Masafumi Takada
